Description:

Located in the heart of Keilor Village, this fully optioned family home on land 950m2 approx. offering 3 bedrooms (BIRs) plus study (4th bedroom), ensuite, WIR to master, huge open plan lounge/dining and spacious family area with spectacular views. Updated modern kitchen with Caesarstone benchtops and Blanco appliances. Downstairs laundry, utility room pool shower and toilet plus double car garage. Surrounded by landscaped gardens, in ground heated pool and spa. Includes gas ducted heating, cooling, vacc maid and much more.

Description:
Quality Family Residence With Great Space And Glorious Parkland Views
Bathed in sunlight, this contemporary two storey family home boasts amazing views combined with spacious areas perfect for families. With a billiards room and media room (projector and screen) ready for watching your favourites, polished floors sweep to the generous open plan living and dining zones with open fireplace. Indulge in the huge chef's kitchen boasting Granite benchtops (echoed in upstairs bathrooms), DeLonghi oven and dual dishwashers, spilling out to an alfresco deck with a swimming pool overlooking the park, great for summer entertaining. Head upstairs to a sunny second living zone/kid's retreat and three large bedrooms (BIRs) share a central bathroom (semi-ensuite access to one), while the main 4th bedroom boasts walk in robe and ensuite (spa bath). Enjoy remote double lock up garage (internal access), alarm, powder room, ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, all close to Green Gully Reserve, Overnewton College and Keilor Village.

Description:
Fabulous Family Entertaining Awaits
Entertainers will delight in sun drenched spaces perfect to host family and friends. Located in a quiet cul-de-sac over two sprawling levels, this modern family home offers a choice of living zone options. A formal living (vaulted ceilings) and dining room flow to a generous chef's kitchen with smart slate flooring and a huge island bench, the perfect place to mingle. A sun filled rumpus flows out to an easy care garden, with a cubby and sandpit to entertain the kids, as you watch from a private alfresco area. Retire to your spacious parent's haven (WIR, ensuite), whilst three further peaceful bedrooms (BIRs) share a choice of two bathrooms (one with spa). With study, hydronic panel heating, split system air conditioning, ceiling fans and double garage (yard access), this immaculate family home is close to Keilor Village, Keilor Primary, Overnewton College, local bike tracks and Brimbank Park.

Description:
In a class of its own!
Rarely do we find a home that offers so much, practically everything a growing family needs. Downstairs the warmth of the polished floor boards gently guide you through the home. The lounge area is found adjacent to the meals area which is flooded by natural sunlight that beams through the bay windows. The fully renovated gallery style kitchen is finished with Caesar Stone bench tops, glass splash backs and ample cupboards would make any chef envious. Upstairs incorporates grand master bedroom with ensuite and walk in robe, three generous bedrooms all with built in robes and centralized main bathroom. Downstairs we find a home office/study, bathroom and rumpus/ 5th bedroom if need be. Outdoors we find a large under cover decked pergola, quaint cottage court yard and a veggie garden. Let's not forget the spacious two car garage. They don't build them like this anymore.
All this in quiet court location and in close proximity to prestigious schooling, major arterials leading to Airports and Melbourne CBD.

Description:
GREat I'm Sold
This perfect family home will tick all the boxes. Perfectly located in a blue ribbon location of Calder Rise close to all the things you may need.
Comprising light filled lounge/dining, well appointed kitchen overlooking the large backyard, meals area & adjoining family room, three generous bedrooms, master with ensuite and BIR. Great outdoor entertaining area with pergola and covered courtyard.
Extras include double carport, gas ducted heating, split system cooling and shed.
Ideally located walking distance to Keilor Village, local Schools, parks, easy access to Calder Freeway, Melbourne CBD and Tullamarine Airport.
So many options, don't miss out. Inspect now.
For more information please call 8744 3211

Description:
If Privacy Is Your Style
This country lifestyle property positioned right next to Keilor village, flanked by the Maribyrnong River offers a tranquil setting to balance a busy lifestyle. Set on 6.25 acres approx the property planted with 350 Arbiquina olive trees could be utilised as a great hobby farm. The original homestead and existing home are situated to take advantage of views over the river and down the valley. 2 bedrooms with BIR's, lounge, central bathroom and large verandah. Add to this a secure gated entry, water pumping facilities (12 meg pumping allocation), town water, easy access to Keilor village, Calder Highway, Melbourne Airport and the CBD.
